    <refsection id="Example_MATDIV">
        <title>Example</title>
        <programlisting role="example">
            A=[1 7 3;23 32 29]
            B=[21 18 34;13 10 19;11 54 36]
            then the result of the x*B=A equation is (A/B):
            x=[-0.475 0.712 0.156;-4.350 8.381 0.491]
        </programlisting>
    </refsection>
